\par <h> 1. Introduction </h>
\par }{\fs24\lang2057 <#/>
Tanzania has a long history of imposed constitutions. <#/>It will be remembered that the terms of reference of the Ormsby-Gore Commission (of 1926). <#/>Which sought to unite Tanganyika with Kenya was rejected by the African Association and prominent Chie
